[[File:Pannonian_Basin.svg|right]]與[[特兰西瓦尼亚高原|外西凡尼亞高原]]包圍]]
[[File:Carpathian_Basin-Pannonian_Basin.jpg|right]]
'''潘諾尼亞平原'''（{{lang-de|Pannonische Tiefebene}}），又稱'''喀爾巴阡盆地'''（{{lang-hu|Kárpát-medence}}）及'''潘諾尼亞盆地'''，<ref>{{cite book |author1=Eldridge M. Moores |author2=Rhodes Whitmore Fairbridge |title = Encyclopedia of European and Asian Regional Geology|publisher = Springer |year= 1997 |isbn = 978-0-412-74040-4 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=Adami Jordan |author2=Peter Jordan |author3=Milan Orožen Adamič |title = Exonyms and the International Standardisation of Geographical Names: Approaches Towards the Resolution of an Apparent Contradiction|publisher = LIT Verlag Berlin-Hamburg-Münster |year = 2007 |pages= 240|isbn = 978-3-8258-0035-2 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author1=George Walter Hoffman |author2=Christopher Shane Davies |title = A Geography of Europe: Problems and Prospects|publisher = Wiley |year = 1983 |pages= 647|isbn = 978-0-471-89708-8 |language=en}}
</ref><ref>
{{cite book 
|author1=George Walter Hoffman |author2=Nels August Bengtson |title= A Geography of Europe|publisher= Ronald Press Co. 
|year= 1953 |pages=757|isbn=|language=en
}}
</ref>是[[歐洲|歐洲]]一大[[平原|平原]]，分屬[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]]、[[捷克|捷克]]、[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]、[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]和[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]。周邊地區包括[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]和[[波斯尼亞|波斯尼亞]]。

潘諾尼亞平原屬於[[阿爾卑斯帶|阿爾卑斯-喜馬拉雅山帶]]子系統，[[上新世|上新世]]時為淺海[[潘諾尼亞海|潘諾尼亞海]]，[[沉積物|沉積物]]達3~4千米<ref>{{cite book |author1=Leigh H. Royden |author2=Ferenc Horváth |title=The Pannonian Basin: A Study in Basin Evolution |publisher=American Association of Petroleum Geologists |year=1988 |isbn=9781629811345 |url=https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/books/book/1357/The-Pannonian-BasinA-Study-in-Basin-Evolution |access-date=2021-05-27 |archive-date=2021-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614133908/https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/books/book/1357/The-Pannonian-BasinA-Study-in-Basin-Evolution |dead-url=no }}</ref>
。在[[馬札兒人|馬札兒人]]轉向定居前,這里是游牧民族生活的地方。

